text: Donald Jay Gaetz ( ; born January 22, 1948) is an American businessman and Republican politician. He is a member of the Florida State Senate since 2024. He was a member before from 2006 to 2016. He was Senate president from 2012 to 2014. Gaetz was elected back to 1st Senate district in the 2024 election. He is the father of former Congressman Matt Gaetz. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Politicians from North Dakota Category:Members of the Florida Legislature
